from cdktf import TerraformStack 
from constructs import Construct 
class API(TerraformStack): 
 def __init__(self, scope: Construct, id: str):
 super().__init__(scope, id)
 # Add API Resources here
class Networking(TerraformStack): 
 def __init__(self, scope: Construct, id: str):
 super().__init__(scope, id)
 # Add Networking Resources here
This is the base 
class for all stacks.
We import Construct for 
our stack's constructor.
Stacks are classes that 
inherit from TerraformStack.
Multiple stacks can be 
defined in a project.
